attributes.title: FINAL COW CHOP CHRISTMAS
attributes.caption: IS THIS EVEN A GIFT?!?!?!?
attributes.description: The final Christmas with Cow Chop is upon us.  But how can we show the love and respect we have gained for each other over the years (or months) that we have been working together?  Why with monetary objects of course!!! Only the best gifts were bought for the best workers in the world.  So what is our worth in presents?  Let's find out one last time!

attributes.title: FISHING TRIP GETAWAY
attributes.caption: THERE'S A MOUSE!!
attributes.description: Well the warehouse is empty. The computers have been shut off.  The doors have been locked, but the mess is still there.  After a great run with Cow Chop, we needed a little getaway to ease our minds into the transfer of joblessness.  So we went north and found a little lake to do some fishing and let off a little steam.  A perfectly calm getaway where nothing chaotic could or would happen.  Right?
